} // --snip-- impl Worker { fn new(id: usize, receiver: Arc<Mutex<mpsc::Receiver<Message>>>) -> Worker { let thread = thread::spawn(move ||{ loop { let message = receiver.lock().unwrap().recv().unwrap(); match message { Message::NewJob(job) => { println!("Worker {} got a job; executing.", id); job.call_box(); }, Message::Terminate => { // ワーカー{}は停止するよう指示された println!("Worker {} was told to terminate.", id); break; }, } } }); Worker { id, thread: Some(thread), } }
